alertmanager_alerts_invalid_total.help: The total number of received alerts that were invalid.

alertmanager_alerts_received_total.help: The total number of received alerts.

alertmanager_build_info.help: A metric with a constant '1' value labeled by version, revision, branch, and goversion from which alertmanager was built.

alertmanager_cluster_enabled.help: Indicates whether the clustering is enabled or not.

alertmanager_config_hash.help: Hash of the currently loaded alertmanager configuration.

alertmanager_config_last_reload_success_.help: Timestamp of the last successful configuration reload.

alertmanager_config_last_reload_successf.help: Whether the last configuration reload attempt was successful.

alertmanager_dispatcher_alert_processing.help: Summary of latencies for the processing of alerts.

alertmanager_http_concurrency_limit_exce.help: Total number of times an HTTP request failed because the concurrency limit was reached.

alertmanager_http_request_duration_secon.help: Histogram of latencies for HTTP requests.
